{
  "texts": [
    "V-BAOs, T -BAOs).Not only are possibility frames semantically equivalent to their underlying BAOs, but also morphisms between possibility frames transform into morphisms between their underlying BAOs in the other direction.",
    "Compare this with the analogous standard results for world frames and their underlying BAOs in, e.g., Goldblatt 1974, Thm.",
    "1.5.9 or Blackburn et al. 2001, Props.",
    "5.51, 5.79.",
    "Theorem 5.9 (From Possibility Morphisms to BAO-Homomorphisms)."
  ]
}